            "title": "即月期指開報25880點 低水48點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指開報25880點，跌51點，較上日現貨收市價25928點低水48點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月科指期貨開報5596點，跌21點，低水22點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月國指期貨開報9136點，跌29點，低水26點。</p>\n</div>",
